  "text": "Let g ij (t) be the data rate from sensor i to j at time t ( i, j \u2208 N, i \u2260 j ). Specifically, g i0 (t) represents the data rate from sensor i to the sink. Then, the flow conservation equation at sensor i can be presented as [CITATION_1] :",
